    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Barns built for storing agricultural produce, taxes, or other contributions paid in support of religious establishments or parishes; common in England.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
